---
title: Minute Steak Ciabatta with Fried Potatoes Three Steps | Ready in 10
description: Sometimes, only a steak sandwich will do. This comfort food of the highest order, and it tastes delicious. Made with flash-in-the-pan steaks and topped with a sweet and spicy mustard dressing, our steak sandwich with fried potatoes is the perfect mid-week recipe.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/steak-sandwich-with-fried-potatoes-8c05fbba-dc7c1d38.jpg
